1
00:01:51,359 --> 00:01:53,000
What is he doing?

2
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:55,439
Don't disturb him.

3
00:01:56,439 --> 00:01:57,239
Teacher Tong.

4
00:01:57,640 --> 00:01:59,480
Our boss is just too busy.

5
00:02:00,319 --> 00:02:01,319
However, Teacher Tong's script...

6
00:02:01,319 --> 00:02:03,040
We have discussed it carefully.

7
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:06,159
I won't talk about the strengths.

8
00:02:06,159 --> 00:02:07,519
Let me just talk about the shortcomings.

9
00:02:07,519 --> 00:02:08,759
Okay, sure.

10
00:02:08,759 --> 00:02:10,080
Better to talk about the strengths first.

11
00:02:13,439 --> 00:02:15,080
Anyone can pick out flaws, right?

12
00:02:15,919 --> 00:02:16,599
Xiao Ma.

13
00:02:16,599 --> 00:02:20,000
Should I drink some water now?

14
00:02:20,439 --> 00:02:22,639
Go on, keep talking.

15
00:02:22,639 --> 00:02:24,680
Teacher Tong, you've always written slice-of-life dramas, right?

16
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:25,199
Yes.

17
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:27,560
So you might not be very familiar...

18
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:28,599
with current mainstream trends.

19
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:31,479
First, your romance plotline is cliche.

20
00:02:31,479 --> 00:02:32,080
Also,

21
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:34,080
the sweet moments, heart-fluttering moments, kissing scenes, heart-wrenching moments are all insufficient.

22
00:02:34,599 --> 00:02:36,479
Five sweet, three heart-fluttering, one heart-wrenching, one kiss per episode...

23
00:02:36,479 --> 00:02:37,520
That's the standard.

24
00:02:37,759 --> 00:02:38,960
Also, Teacher Tong,

25
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:40,719
your "satisfaction factor" isn't strong enough.

26
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:42,280
One can also tell, Teacher Tong,

27
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:43,360
that you haven't dated much.

28
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:44,800
Even my grandma doesn't do it like this anymore.

29
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:47,599
When the leads meet, there must be a smoldering gaze.

30
00:02:47,599 --> 00:02:48,759
I don't see it.

31
00:02:49,439 --> 00:02:51,520
Actually, this genre has its formulas.

32
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:53,240
Like the daily life of a CEO...

33
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:54,439
what he's like,

34
00:02:54,439 --> 00:02:56,280
how he talks, how he acts.

35
00:02:57,039 --> 00:02:58,840
You should read more works in this area.

36
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:01,199
And this business rivalry...

37
00:03:01,199 --> 00:03:02,360
isn't very exciting either.

38
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:04,280
I mean, one can tell...

39
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:04,919
your team probably...

40
00:03:04,919 --> 00:03:07,000
doesn't have much exposure to business wars.

41
00:03:07,599 --> 00:03:08,960
You're not very knowledgeable about this area.

42
00:03:11,199 --> 00:03:12,879
Are you all experts on business wars?

43
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:17,759
Get me...

44
00:03:17,759 --> 00:03:19,319
some water, add some water.

45
00:03:21,199 --> 00:03:22,199
Every one of our editors...

46
00:03:22,199 --> 00:03:23,759
reads a huge number of novels daily.

47
00:03:24,199 --> 00:03:25,879
We must be very familiar with every trope.

48
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:27,080
Teacher Tong,

49
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:29,159
look at our current script here...

50
00:03:29,159 --> 00:03:30,479
Even a basic comeuppance scene...

51
00:03:30,479 --> 00:03:31,599
hasn't been written.

52
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,560
This is definitely not acceptable.

53
00:03:33,639 --> 00:03:35,479
We can't approve this.

54
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:40,199
Hey, what...

55
00:03:40,199 --> 00:03:41,240
are you looking for?

56
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:44,159
Under the bed.

57
00:03:44,159 --> 00:03:45,719
No one can hide here.

58
00:03:45,719 --> 00:03:47,280
I can't meet with her.

59
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:50,240
No, Qianqian is here to discuss business with me, right?

60
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:51,879
What are you doing here causing trouble?

61
00:03:51,879 --> 00:03:54,039
Big brother, you're too naive.

62
00:03:54,159 --> 00:03:55,400
Do you think she's still that...

63
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:56,919
white lotus from the old alleyway?

64
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:58,719
She's backed by big capital now.

65
00:03:58,719 --> 00:04:00,280
She cut ties with everyone long ago.

66
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:01,919
Without me watching, you'll definitely get the short end.

67
00:04:01,919 --> 00:04:03,800
Is it really that bad?

68
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:06,280
And you claim to keep up with the times.

69
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:07,360
Online...

70
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:09,639
